  <div class="card-body bg-dark">
    <div class="jumbotron">
      <h1 class="display-4 text-white">Olá, mundo!</h1>
      <p class="lead text-white">Blog feito com Node, Bootstrap, Mongo e outras ferramentas, blog 100% funcional</p>
      <hr class="my-4">
